## Usage
The first thing is bypass Cloudflare's anti-bot page, all the content access need with [session](#session).

```javascript
import jav from 'javlibrary-api';

jav.config(
    {
        headers: {
            'User-Agent': 'required'
            'Cookie': 'required'
        }
    }
);

(
    async() => {
        var res = await jav.getVideoDetail('javliida3q');
        console.log(res);
    }
)();
```

